1) качаем virtualbox
2) устанавливаем virtualbox

(если не ставиться из-за security)
Open up System Preferences
Click on the Security & Privacy icon
Make sure Allow apps downloaded from: App store and identified developers is checked.

1) нажимаем new
2) create a virtual hard disk now
3) type hard disk -> VDI (VirtualBox Disk Image)
4) storage -> dynamically allocated

